{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe27e14247","title":"为翻译《斯大林全集》给斯大林的电报皖","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a029cb5022","index":0,"year":1951,"month":4,"day":7,"articleId":"fe27e14247"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"104340639e","type":"title","text":"为翻译《斯大林全集》给斯大林的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"fe27e14247"},{"id":"793b4f9003","type":"paragraph","text":"菲里波夫同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"fe27e14247"},{"id":"11f984f1ce","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央热烈地希望得到你的允许在北京将《斯大林全集》翻译为中文。我们认为这对于中国共产党和中国劳动人民是一个重大政治事件。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"fe27e14247"},{"id":"292d7f7ca7","type":"paragraph","text":"为了迅速地和正确无误地进行这个工作，我们准备采取下列步骤：（一）组织一个专门的翻译和校订的委员会担任这一工作。（二）与莫斯科外国文书籍出版局中文部密切合作，包括采取分工翻译互相校订的方法。（三）请联共中央指定在北京的适当的苏联同志帮助我们的工作。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"fe27e14247"},{"id":"40fa798c5e","type":"paragraph","text":"如荷允许我们的要求，请即指定一位同志与我们联系，以解决各项技术问题。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"fe27e14247"},{"id":"038078cc0b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"fe27e14247"},{"id":"cff890dfae","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年四月七日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"fe27e14247"}],"page":{"id":"2b4f6c8e5d","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"fe27e14247","start":223,"end":223}}}},"__N_SSG":true}